title: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlights/maps
description: Description: An exception is thrown when exporting data from the attached report.
OB: When attempting to export data from a table that contains highlights or maps, an exception is thrown.
SR:
Steps to Reproduce:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Navigate to a table that contains highlights or maps.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
4. Observe the exception that is thrown.
